382
00:27:35,690 --> 00:27:37,150
I...

383
00:27:37,150 --> 00:27:38,650
I was a man from the very start!

384
00:27:38,650 --> 00:27:41,980
Then...then...then...how come...

385
00:27:41,980 --> 00:27:45,110
Come here. Come here.

386
00:27:45,110 --> 00:27:46,990
Our Master, he...

387
00:27:46,990 --> 00:27:49,130
has a weird hobby.

388
00:27:49,130 --> 00:27:53,880
He let me dress as a woman and live in the Liu's house.

389
00:27:54,400 --> 00:27:56,680
Master?

390
00:27:56,680 --> 00:28:00,000
