509
00:34:32,980 --> 00:34:36,850
Why not let the exceptional Fox Clan rule over all

510
00:34:36,850 --> 00:34:41,150
and save you pitiful villains?

511
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:56,970
<i>Should I try for Madam's room again tonight?</i>

512
00:34:56,970 --> 00:35:00,900
<i>By my count, the three days of abstinence have passed.</i>

513
00:35:03,130 --> 00:35:06,130
<i>Tao Heng, you are nothing.</i>

514
00:35:06,130 --> 00:35:11,180
<i>I won't be satisfied until I get rid of you.</i>

515
00:35:12,820 --> 00:35:14,520
You can't even pour tea now?

516
00:35:14,520 --> 00:35:18,340
I was thinking of what to prepare for you for a night snack.

517
00:35:18,340 --> 00:35:20,600
There's no need.

518
00:35:20,600 --> 00:35:24,160
I will be sleeping in First Mistress' room tonight. Why don't you rest early.

519
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:30,970
What's going on lately?

520
00:35:30,970 --> 00:35:34,740
Rejections all around.

521
00:35:39,970 --> 00:35:44,450
I remember when we were newlyweds, you did this all the time.

522
00:35:44,450 --> 00:35:47,090
Getting water for my wash.

523
00:35:47,090 --> 00:35:50,020
If I didn't see you all day, then

524
00:35:50,020 --> 00:35:52,990
I wouldn't be able to sleep well.

525
00:35:52,990 --> 00:35:57,230
Good times will always fade away.

526
00:35:57,230 --> 00:36:00,930
Since then, even without me,

527
00:36:00,930 --> 00:36:04,000
weren't you just fine?

528
00:36:04,930 --> 00:36:06,340
Madam!

529
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:12,050
It's all my fault. I shouldn't have looked for something new and married Ying'er.

530
00:36:12,050 --> 00:36:14,150
I neglected you.

531
00:36:17,120 --> 00:36:19,340
It isn't all your fault.

532
00:36:19,340 --> 00:36:22,770
I didn't bear the Hong family a boy or a girl.

533
00:36:22,770 --> 00:36:26,490
-I almost violated the seven rules<br>- No! no!

534
00:36:26,500 --> 00:36:28,290
It was all my foolishness.

535
00:36:28,290 --> 00:36:29,960
Will you give me another chance?

536
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:32,420
Will you forgive me?

537
00:36:37,720 --> 00:36:41,490
Then...can we rest now?

538
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:34,710
Where did this chicken come from?

539
00:37:34,710 --> 00:37:36,970
I saw that you haven't eaten these couple of days,

540
00:37:36,970 --> 00:37:40,460
so I had Su Xi buy it from the villagers.

541
00:37:48,690 --> 00:37:50,980
What... What is it?

542
00:37:58,510 --> 00:38:00,610
What are you doing?

543
00:38:00,610 --> 00:38:04,700
I...I... Nothing.

544
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:09,970
The chicken is cooked!

545
00:38:09,970 --> 00:38:11,160
-Really?<br>-I'll tear you a piece

546
00:38:11,160 --> 00:38:12,850
Wonderful!

547
00:38:17,030 --> 00:38:19,060
Here, have a taste.

548
00:38:19,830 --> 00:38:22,140
Is it good?

549
00:38:24,050 --> 00:38:26,960
<i>Mistress Nine-tail is so adorable!</i>

550
00:38:28,140 --> 00:38:30,940
<i>Oh heavens, what am I doing now?</i>

551
00:38:30,940 --> 00:38:32,650
<i>Have I gone crazy?</i>

552
00:38:32,650 --> 00:38:36,930
<i>Have I developed feelings for my senior?</i>

553
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:39,880
<i>Where is your sense?</i>

554
00:38:39,880 --> 00:38:41,740
<i>Liu Changyan!</i>

555
00:38:42,500 --> 00:38:44,650
Aren't you eating?

556
00:38:44,650 --> 00:38:46,760
Yes! I'm eating, I'm eating!

557
00:38:48,080 --> 00:38:50,540
Eating!

558
00:38:51,290 --> 00:38:53,590
Delicious!

559
00:38:55,200 --> 00:38:59,130
<i>I guess my senses, from the time in the mountains when she started tormenting me,</i>

560
00:38:59,130 --> 00:39:01,560
<i>have been lost</i>

561
00:39:08,270 --> 00:39:11,000
It smells wonderful!

562
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,650
You ate it all!

563
00:39:12,650 --> 00:39:14,840
And left me the chicken's butt!

564
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:20,670
What noise is that!

565
00:39:20,670 --> 00:39:23,140
Quick, let's hide.

566
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:39,370
What are you doing?

567
00:39:39,370 --> 00:39:42,190
-My power isn't working!<br>-Not working?

568
00:39:42,190 --> 00:39:43,940
Get behind me.

569
00:39:45,050 --> 00:39:46,990
Hide.

570
00:39:48,600 --> 00:39:52,920
Who is the bastard Liu Changyan? Come out and die!

571
00:39:55,160 --> 00:39:57,130
It's your responsibility to protect the clan leader, right?

572
00:39:57,130 --> 00:39:59,020
Go out, go!

573
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:03,700
Sir, he is Liu Changyan! We're all just servants.

574
00:40:03,700 --> 00:40:05,110
Please let us go!

575
00:40:05,110 --> 00:40:06,680
What are you talking about?

576
00:40:06,680 --> 00:40:09,290
You are Liu Changyan?

577
00:40:09,290 --> 00:40:12,950
Sir, the one who is sleeping in there is Mrs. Liu.

578
00:40:12,950 --> 00:40:14,850
Please let us go.

579
00:40:14,850 --> 00:40:17,010
You, go!

580
00:40:17,010 --> 00:40:19,180
You, tie him up!

581
00:40:21,890 --> 00:40:23,660
Let's go!

582
00:40:24,310 --> 00:40:26,910
Yo! You look really pretty!

583
00:40:26,910 --> 00:40:29,020
Let me touch you...

584
00:40:43,790 --> 00:40:45,700
Open your mouth!

585
00:40:45,700 --> 00:40:47,760
Do it quickly! I don't want new problems to rise!

586
00:40:47,760 --> 00:40:49,160
Let's go!

587
00:40:49,160 --> 00:40:52,240
Go! Go! Quickly!

588
00:40:56,830 --> 00:40:59,950
Go! Quickly!

589
00:41:04,080 --> 00:41:06,130
Heng'er, are you alright?

590
00:41:06,130 --> 00:41:08,070
What can go wrong for me?

591
00:41:09,410 --> 00:41:12,800
I feel like there's something unusual about these thugs.

592
00:41:14,830 --> 00:41:18,730
You just said your magic doesn't work anymore. Why is that so?

593
00:41:18,730 --> 00:41:22,210
I have no idea. That never happened before.

594
00:41:22,210 --> 00:41:26,390
But even if my magic doesn't work, we can still use your magic.

595
00:41:26,390 --> 00:41:30,200
We're not allowed to use magic in the human world.

596
00:41:30,200 --> 00:41:33,050
Didn't you already use it just then?

597
00:41:33,610 --> 00:41:36,070
That... That was an emergency.

598
00:41:36,070 --> 00:41:38,710
There's order in the human world. We can't disrupt it.

599
00:41:38,710 --> 00:41:40,590
What rule is that?

600
00:41:40,590 --> 00:41:45,420
The 93-rule of the fox clan. Any fox traveling in the human world cannot use magic.

601
00:41:45,420 --> 00:41:48,880
Anyone who disrupts the order of the human world will stay in the human world forever

602
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:51,030
and cannot go back to the Green Hill.

603
00:41:51,030 --> 00:41:55,810
Senior, you are a nine-tail-fox. Only nine-tail-foxes won't be restricted by the rules of the fox clan.

604
00:41:55,810 --> 00:41:59,020
I wonder who set that rule.

605
00:41:59,020 --> 00:42:01,550
The elders and my father.

606
00:42:01,550 --> 00:42:04,690
The son is just like his father. I finally understand that phrase now.

607
00:42:04,690 --> 00:42:07,110
Okay, let's stop talking about these useless things.

608
00:42:07,110 --> 00:42:10,810
We have to think of a way to untie these ropes.

609
00:42:11,310 --> 00:42:12,970
But they are too tight.

610
00:42:12,970 --> 00:42:15,770
How can we untie them if we cannot use our magic?

611
00:42:15,770 --> 00:42:17,460
Untie...?

612
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:22,870
What are you doing?

613
00:42:28,120 --> 00:42:32,840
<i>Nine-tail-fox, as long as you can be heartbroken like the other foxes,</i>

614
00:42:32,840 --> 00:42:36,500
<i>and give me one teardrop,</i>

615
00:42:36,500 --> 00:42:40,360
<i>this magical fruit will ripen.</i>

616
00:42:42,200 --> 00:42:45,150
<i>-Grey-eared-fox?<br>-You destroyed my face and my eye,</i>

617
00:42:45,150 --> 00:42:46,920
<i>and forced me to cut my own tail...</i>

618
00:42:46,920 --> 00:42:50,280
<i>Today, I'm going to make you pay twice the price!</i>

619
00:42:50,280 --> 00:42:51,970
<i>Oh woman!</i>

620
00:42:51,970 --> 00:42:54,810
<i>Won't you drop even one tear for him?</i>

621
00:42:54,810 --> 00:42:56,540
<i>Look at him.</i>

622
00:42:57,560 --> 00:42:59,750
<i>Die!</i>

